  <p>
    If you ask three companies for a "septic inspection," you may get three quite different services —
    and that's not a sign of anything shady, it's just that the word covers a wide range. An inspection
    can be a brief visual look or a comprehensive functional evaluation, and everything in between.
    Understanding the spectrum lets you get the depth your situation actually needs and compare quotes
    fairly.
  </p>

  {/* Intended asset: /images/resources/what-may-be-included-in-a-septic-inspection-hero.webp — see public/images/resources/README.md */}
